  • \[ Log(ab) = Log(a) + Log(b) \]
  • \[ Log(\frac{a}{b}) = Log(a) - Log(b) \]
  • \[ Log(a^2) = 2*Log(a) \]

  • \[ Log(a^3b^2) = 3*Log(a) + 2*Log(b) \]

\[ V = L^3 ; A = L^2 ; A = V^\frac{2}{3} \] \[ Brain^3 = Body^2 ; Brain = Body^\frac{2}{3} \] \[ Log(\frac{Brain^3}{Body^2}) = 3*Log(Brain) - 2*Log(Body) \]
